{"tid":1281110,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"9成男仔都係笠水狗","createTime":"2019-07-03T07:51:00.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-03T08:06:10.000Z","uid":169960,"like":19,"dislike":56,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"5d02a46260231891cfad1ad12f2b31bee01c28ef","tid":1281110,"uid":169960,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T07:51:00.000Z","msg":"發夢喺龍和最前線 見到啲男仔帶晒頭盔企到勁後 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n喺前排有三分之一都係女仔仲要冇頭盔...<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n其實驚個個都驚 你唔想企前面冇人怪你 <br />\n<br />\n但麻煩傳返啲頭盔去前面一二排啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我喺個晚龍和道企第二排嘅女仔 <br />\n<br />\n其實我驚到仆街 後面都有人傳頭盔俾我戴<br />\n<br />\n但前面第一排仲有好多人未有頭盔<br />\n<br />\n所以唔該你哋企咁後唔好浪費晒啲物資<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n你驚 仲有大把人驚過你"},{"pid":"3309f8db464b1c93ae4093e4b91774a81d929bd0","tid":1281110,"uid":103887,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T07:51:27.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"4bfa2bd8250a4ec297275f1d6f402f5a83f1db1f","tid":1281110,"uid":60545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T07:52:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"09c923e3ab8a781655f122801f449dff7424b700","tid":1281110,"uid":195252,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T07:53:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cc4b46300916094b8c71d5c24b8205ecc639ef73","tid":1281110,"uid":51701,"like":22,"dislike":0,"score":22,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T07:53:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5AZPCNr.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5AZPCNr.jpg&h=398a4bbd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n唔係話唔信你"},{"pid":"839fa7a6539dddbb1f0000e4b0ebede4a06744c4","tid":1281110,"uid":60545,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1